Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.90,0:14:33.68,Default,Superior,0,0,0,,{Your sales for this month were the \Nlowest on the team, Gotoh-san.}Doanh số bán hàng tháng này thấp nhất là chị Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.74,Default,Colleague 1,0,0,0,,{Gotoh-san again?}Lại là Gotoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.57,Default,Colleague 2,0,0,0,,{It's partly the boss being cruel.}Giám đốc lại chèn ép nữa rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:41.19,Default,Colleague 2,0,0,0,,{He transferred her to sales \Nto try to make her quit!}Chuyển cô ta đến bộ phận sales để cho nghỉ việc sớm mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.94,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\3c&H7F7877&\c&H232623&\bord2\pos(320,239)\frx26\fry0}{Tokoroten}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:44.09,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me...}A-À vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:46.53,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Would you like to buy some tokoroten?}Q-Quý khách có muốn mua tokoroten không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.56,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's well-aged, and it goes down smooth...}Nó là hàng lâu năm và rất dễ nuốt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.86,Default,Solicited Man,0,0,0,,{No, thank you!}Không!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,126)}{Transferred to\Nsales department}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,210.5)}{Fail at door-\Nto-door sales}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:54.87,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1572,1)\bord2\fnTimes New Roman\fs16\c&HB0C8C1&\3c&H55569D&\pos(559,308.5)}{Stress quit and\N become a shut-in}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.87,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I see as plain as day \Nwhere my Game of Life is going!}Mình đã biết trước cái trò chơi cuộc\N đời khốn khổ của bản thân!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.87,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Hitori-chan, won't you open up? Please?}Hitori này, mở cửa ra đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:15:00.37,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{You don't have to go back to work.}Con không cần đi làm nữa đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.87,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Just come eat dinner with me again!}Xuống ăn tối với gia đình nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:03.71,Default,Michiyo,0,0,0,,{Please?}Làm ơn đi.
