Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:09.68,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Another of Bocchi-chan's episodes?}Lại mộng tưởng của Bocchi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.39,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, so that }{\i1}{is}{\i0}{ typical for her!}Như mọi khi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:15.02,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{If I can't make money with my guitar, \NI'll end up a NEET.}Nếu không thể kiếm tiền bằng ghita, \Nmình sẽ trở thành NEET.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:16.97,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Her face is scary when it gets like that.}Mỗi khi như thế thì mặt em ấy đáng sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.97,DefaultTop,Hitori,0,0,0,,{If I can't make money with my guitar...}Nếu không thể làm ra tiền bằng ghita...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:20.30,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{Really? I think it's got personality.}Thế hả? Tớ thì thấy nó khá độc đáo mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.48,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Are you for real?}Thật luôn?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.30,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sandpaper, please.}Đưa chị tờ giấy nhám!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It's kind of a chore, huh?}Lần nào cũng phiền hết nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.59,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Whoops. Think I botched it.}Chết! Hình như chà hơi quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{It's okay.}Không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.21,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Just do it like this. See?}Chị chà thêm chỗ này nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.24,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{They're used to it!}Quen rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.90,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Up we go.}Lên nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:35.93,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Did I make her face too long?}Hình như mặt hơi dài?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.21,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I think it's about right.}Em nghĩ vậy là đúng rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:40.34,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, thank you!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.63,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{A-Actually can I fix it up a little?}T-Thôi để em sửa lại xíu nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.36,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{By the way, Ikuyo.}Cơ mà Ikuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:53.55,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{You played pretty well today for only \Nhaving done this for three months.}Em đã chơi rất tốt dù chỉ mới 3 tháng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:57.76,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Huh? Who's Ikuyo again?}Ikuyo là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:02.78,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Dunno! Who'd have a crummy \Nold name like that?!}E-Em cũng chả biết, cái tên nghe như bà già đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.15,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{It's }{\i1}{your}{\i0}{ name, isn't it?!}Tên em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.49,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's Kita-chan's name?}Tên của Kita-chan à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.00,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{That face is contagious, huh?}Mặt Bocchi có tính lây lan hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:11.39,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I hid it for so long!}Em đã giấu rồi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.32,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{I hate my name so much!}Em không thích cái tên đó đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.41,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{How come? It's cute.}Sao thế? Dễ thương mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.39,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{You wouldn't understand, \Nsince you have a beautiful name}Chị sẽ không hiểu vì chị có cái tên đẹp
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.00,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{that means "song of the stars"!}mang nghĩa "bài hát của những ngôi sao" đó đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:21.37,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Look at her freak out!}Em ấy đang bối rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.78,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{But mine sounds like a bad pun!}Của em nghe như mấy trò cười nhàm chán vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.97,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{"Kita! Ikuyo!" (I'm here! Let's go!)}"Kita Ikuyo!" *Tớ đến rồi, đi thôi"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.37,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{Are you serious?!}Nghe ngu ngốc ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.84,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{I think we broke her.}Em ấy sắp vỡ tan rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:33.66,Default,Kita,0,0,0,,{My full name is Kita Kita.}Tên của em là Kita Kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.84,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Seeing you withdraw into your shell is fun.}Thấy em chui vào vỏ ốc thật thú vị mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.39,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{You're sadistic.}Em xấu tính quá đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.59,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{So, as for what you were saying before...}Như chị nói lúc trước...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:46.77,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{You were mumbling about supporting yourself \Nwith the guitar and becoming a NEET.}Em lầm bầm về vụ ghita rồi trở thành NEET...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.20,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry for losing my head...}E-Em xin lỗi vì mất đi ý thức...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.36,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, nothin' wrong with it.}Không phải chuyện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.36,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{But lemme give you some advice \Nas your senpai in the world of bands.}Nhưng để chị chỉ em với tư cách là đàn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.49,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Just chill out and enjoy yourself!}Cứ tận hưởng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.41,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{If you put the weight of success \Non your own shoulders all the time,}Nếu cứ mãi nghĩ đến thành công,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:05.28,Default,PA,0,0,0,,{you'll just make yourself miserable.}thì em sẽ rất khổ sở đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.59,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Phải phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:10.25,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{It's important to enjoy the process \Nof making your dream come true.}Quan trọng là tận hưởng giấc mơ của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:14.98,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{By the way, Senpai, how come \Nyou suddenly quit playing?}Cơ mà sao tự nhiên chị nghỉ ban nhạc vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Th-The manager was in a band?}Q-Quản lý từng ở trong ban nhạc sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.64,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, yah. They were }{\i1}{super}{\i0}{ popular.}Phải đó, nổi tiếng lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.92,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Then wh-why...}V-Vậy tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:24.85,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,Mệt mỏi chứ sao.{I got sick of bands.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.06,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{But you run a club. \NWhat's the deal there, huh?}Nhưng chị vẫn mở Club mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.38,DefaultTop,Seika,0,0,0,,Im mồm và uống đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Nijika-chan never said a word about that...}Mình chưa từng nghe chị Nijika nói gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:32.47,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,Uống thêm được ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Ủa? Chị ấy đi đâu nãy giờ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.07,DefaultTop,Seika,0,0,0,,Tự trả phần mình đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.53,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0,0,0,,Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:37.84,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me.}E-Em xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.45,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I have to use the restroom.}Em đi vệ sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.70,Default,Kikuri,0,0,0,,{Manager, keep 'em comin'!}Quản lý, tiếp tục uống đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:51.63,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me... Nijika-chan?}C-Chị Nijika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.64,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Oh, Bocchi-chan!}Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.59,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-Is something the matter?}C-Có chuyện gì ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:58.34,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Nah, just getting some fresh air.}Hít thở khí trời thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:01.79,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-It's been getting cold \Nat night lately, huh?}G-Gần đây trời đêm hơi lạnh nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Sure has.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.64,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Next thing we know, \Nsummer break's gonna be over!}Chưa gì mùa hè đã kết thúc rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:09.89,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I hear nothing.}Không nghe thấy gì hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.23,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I know nothing.}Không biết gì hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.84,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Summer break never ends.}Mùa hè không kết thúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.56,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm not a student.}Mình không phải sinh viên.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.70,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Trees, water, planets, Milky Way...}Cây cối, nước, hành tinh, thiên hà...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.70,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan! Back to reality!}Bocchi, quay lại hiện thực!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.35,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry.}E-Em xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.46,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:26.08,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Say...}Nè...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:28.83,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I realized something while I was \Nwatching you play today.}Hôm nay nhìn em diễn chị mới nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:32.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You're guitarhero, aren't you?}Em là ghitahero nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.98,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{W-Well, a-actually, n-no, about that...}À t-t-thực ra... k-không...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:43.81,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It was pretty obvious from the \Non-point way you were strumming.}Nghe đoạn gảy đàn đó là chị nhận ra ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:47.06,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And I finally noticed \Nyou had the same guitar.}Cơ mà giờ mới nhận ra ghita cùng loại...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.26,0:18:49.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{No use trying to hide it now.}Không giấu được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.08,0:18:52.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Um...}À..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.40,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I am.}Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:57.36,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-But I didn't hide it on purpose.}N-Nhưng em không giấu giếm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:02.24,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Since I'm anything but a hero right now...}E-Em hiện tại vẫn chưa là hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:05.93,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I w-wanted to wait to tell you \Nuntil I fixed the way I am.}Nên m-muốn chờ thêm một chút mới nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:09.12,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Especially you, Nijika-chan.}Đ-Đặc biệt là chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:15.13,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-Are you shocked to find out?}C-Chị sốc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Nah...}Không...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.30,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It made me all t\he more happy to have you!}Ngược lại còn thấy may mắn chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.01,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:25.31,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{See, I told you I had a dream before, right?}Chị nói với em mình có một giấc mơ, phải chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.26,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes?}V-Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:32.57,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{My mom died when I was little, \Nand my dad was never home,}Mẹ mất khi chị còn nhỏ, ba chị thì ít khi ở nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:35.02,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{so my sister was pretty much my only family.}Nên chị chỉ có chị gái là gia đình.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.66,0:19:40.00,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But since I hated being alone, \Nwhen my sis started a band,}Nhưng khi chị ấy tham gia ban nhạc,\Nvà chị ghét phải ở một mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.79,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I had her take me to her clubs all the time.}Nên ngày nào cũng được dẫn đến xem diễn live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.58,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It all seemed so shining to me.}Lúc đó mọi thứ đều toả sáng với chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I was never happier anywhere else.}Một không gian thật hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:56.50,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I was her inspiration for quitting her band \Nand starting up this club.}Sau khi thấy chị như vậy,\Nchị ấy nghỉ ban nhạc và mở Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:20:02.01,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Starry is a place my sister made for me.}Starry là nơi chị ấy tạo ra cho chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.39,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Though I'll bet she won't admit it.}Dù chị ấy không nói gì về việc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:09.39,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{So my real dream}Nên giấc mơ thực sự của chị
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.89,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{is to make a band popular \Nenough for me and my sister}là biến ban nhạc này trở nên \Nnổi tiếng thay phần chị mình nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:16.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{and make Starry even more famous!}Và giúp Starry trở nên nổi tiếng hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.44,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But when I actually started my band,}Nhưng khi bắt đầu ban nhạc,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:24.45,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I spent a while thinking that \Nit was kind of out of my reach.}chị đã nghĩ nó thật vô vọng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.71,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{And everyone was so disheartened today.}Và mọi người hôm nay ai cũng mất tự tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:33.33,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But every time things \Nare looking their worst,}Nhưng cứ mỗi khi trong tình huống tồi tệ nhất,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.04,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(328.5,113.5)}{Ripe Mangos}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.97,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{you're the one who breaks through it for us!}em lại là người phá vỡ nó và kéo mọi người theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:42.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Bocchi-chan, you were \None heck of a hero to me today.}Hôm nay em là anh hùng của chị đó, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:49.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Ryo wants to use this band to finally \Nget to play music from the heart,}Ryo muốn chơi những bản nhạc từ tận con tim,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.08,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{and Kita-chan wants to really \Ndo something with us.}Kita-chan thì muốn ở cạnh mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:57.25,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{They've all invested their hopes in the band.}Ai cũng đều nuôi hi vọng vào ban nhạc này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:04.66,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That reminds me, you never actually told me \Nwhat you were doing the band for now.}Cơ mà... em tại sao lại tham gia ban nhạc nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.28,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I...}Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:14.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{As a guitarist, I want to make the \NKessoku Band we all care so much about}Là một tay ghita, em muốn ban nhạc Kessoku của chúng ta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:16.50,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{the best band it can be!}trở thành ban nhạc tuyệt vời nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:22.63,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{A-And I want us to become such a popular band}V-Và em muốn trở nên nổi tiếng
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:25.15,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{that we can make money \Nand not have to finish school...}kiếm tiền và không phải đi học nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.99,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{That's a pretty tall order!}Mục tiêu gì thú vị vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:29.34,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But I accept your investment!}Nhưng chị sẽ chấp nhận nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:37.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I sure do wish you could play the way \Nyou do in your videos every time, though...}Chị cũng muốn em chơi như trong video quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.95,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'll d-do my best...}E-Em sẽ cố hết sức...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:44.28,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{But now I know it for sure!}Nhưng có một điều chị chắc chắn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:47.70,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Having you with us will \Nmake our dreams possible!}Có em thì giấc mơ nhất định sẽ thành hiện thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:51.20,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{So keep showing us more and more.}Nên hãy cho bọn chị thấy nhiều hơn nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.95,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Of "Bocchi-chan's rock."}Cái rock của Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.53,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Bocchi the Rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:04.96,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Okay!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:08.30,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\t(30,3325,\fscx93.53\fscy93.53)\c&H07C7F0&\fnImpact\fs36\move(156.5,131,167.16,134.06,30,3325)}{BOCCHI THE ROCK!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:11.30,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with being young?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:10.89,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fscx93.53\t(27,2571,\fscx90.16)\fscy93.53\t(27,2571,\fscy90.16)\c&H07C7F0&\fnImpact\fs36\move(167.16,134.06,172.66,-51.94,27,2571)}{BOCCHI THE ROCK!}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:11.64,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{I hate it when I'm right.}Mình có cảm giác không ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.14,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Hey, why doesn't it stop?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.31,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The rhythm that I can't stop}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:25.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{keeps reverberating through my body}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.19,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The melody playing in my earphones}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.19,0:22:34.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{is the only thing that lets me be who I am}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.20,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{The sky is tinged in red}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:45.00,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But what color is my soul?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.40,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Tell me}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:50.99,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{where should I go?}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.98,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've always been searching}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:57.20,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{for something precious (hey!)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:02.82,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{If everything's going to be lost some day}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.82,0:23:06.09,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{let's engrave it as deep as we can (now!)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:09.50,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{My most pathetic nights \Nand cackling laughter}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:13.68,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And days when I couldn't say \Nmore than "You know..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:17.84,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{(I'm alive now, yeah Springtime of life)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:19.77,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with not \Nletting my sound die down?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.86,Songs_ED_Basic,Hitori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong with being young?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:39.98,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Watch it!}
